textBeforeTable: Career Statistics (Regular Season) Game Log Stats Read more Personal: Son of Barry and Laurie, and has four siblings – McNeil, Colin, Hugh and Grace … Lists his favorite reality TV show as “Survivor” … The best meal Sam cooks is chicken parmesan … If he wasn’t a soccer player, he would be a golfer … Favorite sport other than soccer is tennis … Enjoys watching the NFL and NBA … Favorite vacation spot is the Bahamas … Names the Red Hot Chili Peppers as his favorite music group.
